
yum install zlib-devel gcc make git autoconf autogen automake pkgconfig
2、下载和安装Netdata（需要root权限）
cd /usr/local/src/（自己建的目录也行，不一定在这个目录下面）
wget http://firehol.org/download/netdata/releases/v1.0.0/netdata-1.0.0.tar.gz
tar -xf netdata-1.0.0.tar.gz
cd netdata-1.0.0
./netdata-installer.sh


ok. NetData is installed and is running.

Hit http://localhost:19999/ from your browser.

To stop netdata, just kill it, with:

  killall netdata

To start it, just run it:

  /usr/sbin/netdata

Enjoy!
